                    Go to the QUAN tutoring center in Dwire ( <url href="https://bit.ly/4a4c4rx" />) and/or the Mathematics Excel Center (<url href="https://mathcenter.uccs.edu">https://mathcenter.uccs.edu</url>) for tutoring related to QUAN/statistics topics
